{"tid":2515070,"cid":36,"subCid":0,"title":"如果喊唔出仲算唔算係抑鬱","createTime":"2021-05-03T16:29:48.000Z","updateTime":"2021-05-03T19:10:30.000Z","uid":257896,"like":0,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"098631d449adb23d912be68ccbf9f58e1806c907","tid":2515070,"uid":257896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T16:29:48.000Z","msg":"以前未肯定有抑鬱症嗰陣會成日喊<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n事無大小只要trigger到情緒就會好負面好唔開心係咁喊<br />\n但自從睇醫生食藥開始喊少咗<br />\n到後期真係冇哂情緒成個人好平靜<br />\n冇睇醫生冇食藥之後以為自己已經變得開心咗唔會成日都諗嘢太負面係咁喊<br />\n但呢排壓力好大 個腦停唔到會係咁往負面嘅方向諗<br />\n但點諗都好我都已經再流唔出一滴眼淚<br />\n會手震會心跳加速但都喊唔出<br />\n好似冇咗個宣洩情緒嘅渠道咁<br />\n唔知咁樣算係復發定點<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5ba7f2109c09d06704bb0c3c78ce124cfc81ed44","tid":2515070,"uid":303838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T16:37:40.000Z","msg":"係無左情感or純粹喊唔出呢?<br />\n睇過嚴重抑鬱都可以令到人無左情感"},{"pid":"ab577abb5742fe6877c4fe7958678a5e30cc5788","tid":2515070,"uid":257896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5ba7f2109c09d06704bb0c3c78ce124cfc81ed44","tid":2515070,"uid":303838,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T16:37:40.000Z","msg":"係無左情感or純粹喊唔出呢?<br />\n睇過嚴重抑鬱都可以令到人無左情感"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T16:45:44.000Z","msg":"我諗係純粹喊唔出<br />\n因為睇劇仲識笑<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但除咗睇開心嘢會笑之外都冇乜機會笑<br />\n一諗起生活上嘅好多壓力就好辛苦<br />\n壓力爆煲嗰陣想嗌又嗌唔到（唔想比屋企人知）<br />\n以前仲可以縮喺被竇度喊但依家真係喊唔出<br />\n可能係淚腺有問題<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/crowd.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"eff962965673b7196e06b7485d1fcd296e7e0429","tid":2515070,"uid":128064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T16:55:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得喊唔出衰撚過喊得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9264862a278abc49f14c35aaa728a9cb9b0cce54","tid":2515070,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:18:14.000Z","msg":"唔夠水份<br />\n同無尿屙一樣<br />\n見字飲多啲水"},{"pid":"993c56636322853320bae5a8e30924534e9e5eca","tid":2515070,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:46:03.000Z","msg":"唔開心已經係抑鬱"},{"pid":"97f0bb1e09d56000a767a61ac40b5fddda6010d7","tid":2515070,"uid":257896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"eff962965673b7196e06b7485d1fcd296e7e0429","tid":2515070,"uid":128064,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T16:55:58.000Z","msg":"我覺得喊唔出衰撚過喊得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/bouncy.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T19:01:43.000Z","msg":"有時我覺得係好事嚟<br />\n因為以前喊真係理唔到時地人事<br />\n覺得會麻煩到人同埋好失禮<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但依家只係想喺被竇入面喊下解壓都做唔到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"407c165a67ecaba4af7e8fbda7a4abd0237f433a","tid":2515070,"uid":257896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9264862a278abc49f14c35aaa728a9cb9b0cce54","tid":2515070,"uid":37525,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:18:14.000Z","msg":"唔夠水份<br />\n同無尿屙一樣<br />\n見字飲多啲水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T19:03:03.000Z","msg":"但我好多尿屙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />係啲水份去唔到淚腺咁<br />\nbtw巴打見字都飲多啲水！"},{"pid":"ef5830ca6ea24eaf23438e9cdaf8354c93ba8ca5","tid":2515070,"uid":257896,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"993c56636322853320bae5a8e30924534e9e5eca","tid":2515070,"uid":160964,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T17:46:03.000Z","msg":"唔開心已經係抑鬱"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T19:05:42.000Z","msg":"但好唔開心嘅話係咪應該要喊得出<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n未到喊唔出嘅唔開心好似冇咁嚴重咁"},{"pid":"695fe312b97daf476b16dbcb9da6ceb51cc50c4a","tid":2515070,"uid":295735,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T19:06:21.000Z","msg":"算。重度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5b4e87c23f91adc98ae242e20b562f3df369a0c8","tid":2515070,"uid":174225,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-05-03T19:10:30.000Z","msg":"我覺得喊係好事 可以放晒啲負能量出去<br />\n我都好難喊 可能無咩負能量"}]}